@page "/solutions/retail"
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components

<PageTitle>Retail Stores — DMD StockShopOnline</PageTitle>

<div class="sol-hero">
    <div class="sol-hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-left">
            <div class="sol-eyebrow">
                <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
                Built for retail
            </div>
            <h1 class="sol-title">Your store runs on trust.<br /><span class="sol-accent">Your software should too.</span></h1>
            <p class="sol-sub">Whether you're running a corner shop or a multi-location chain, DMD gives you the tools to stay on top of stock, move customers through quickly, and actually understand your numbers.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="/contact?plan=retail" class="btn-primary">Start free trial</a>
                <a href="/pricing" class="btn-ghost">See pricing</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-right">
            <div class="proof-card">
                <div class="proof-header">
                    <div class="proof-avatar">RS</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="proof-name">Rami S.</div>
                        <div class="proof-role">Owner, convenience store · Montréal</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="proof-quote">"Before DMD I had no idea which products were actually making money. Now I check the profitability report every Monday and it's changed how I order."</p>
                <div class="proof-stat-row">
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">3×</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">faster checkout</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">0</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">manual stock counts</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">14d</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">free to try</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="sol-page">

    <div class="pains-section">
        <div class="pains-label">Sound familiar?</div>
        <div class="pains-grid">
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>You've run out of a fast-moving item because nobody noticed stock getting low</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>Checkout slows down because staff can't find products by name or SKU</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>Month-end means digging through receipts to figure out if you actually made money</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>You can't trust what a part-time cashier rang in while you weren't watching</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="solutions-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Here's how DMD fixes that</h2>
        <div class="sol-cards">

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon teal-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Checkout in seconds</h3>
                <p>Search by name, SKU, or scan a barcode. Add to cart, apply a discount if needed, take payment. Your fastest cashier just got faster — and so did the new hire on their first shift.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Product search</span>
                    <span class="tag">Discounts</span>
                    <span class="tag">Cash &amp; card</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon navy-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M20 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Always know what's on the shelf</h3>
                <p>Every sale deducts from stock automatically. Low stock shows up on your dashboard the moment it crosses the threshold. Run purchase orders to restock before customers notice.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Live stock levels</span>
                    <span class="tag">Low stock alerts</span>
                    <span class="tag">Purchase orders</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon green-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Understand your numbers without an accountant</h3>
                <p>See revenue, expenses, and net income in one view. Product profitability tells you which items to push and which to quietly drop. Export everything to Excel for your bookkeeper.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Financial dashboard</span>
                    <span class="tag">Product profitability</span>
                    <span class="tag">Excel export</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon purple-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Control what your staff can see and do</h3>
                <p>Cashiers get the POS. Managers get reports. You get everything. Role-based access means no accidental deletions, no snooping on financials, and full accountability for every transaction.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Role-based access</span>
                    <span class="tag">Audit trail</span>
                    <span class="tag">Cash sessions</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon orange-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"/><line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Run promotions without the spreadsheet</h3>
                <p>Create a special in 3 steps — pick the products, set the discount, activate it. Promotions auto-apply at checkout so staff don't have to remember what's on sale this week.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Promotions wizard</span>
                    <span class="tag">Auto-apply at POS</span>
                    <span class="tag">Print specials</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon blue-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Canadian taxes, handled correctly</h3>
                <p>GST and PST calculated per product, per province — automatically. No manual tax lookups, no year-end surprises. Your reports already show exactly what you collected.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">GST &amp; PST</span>
                    <span class="tag">Per-product tax</span>
                    <span class="tag">Tax reports</span>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explore-more">
        <h2>Also built for</h2>
        <div class="explore-grid">
            <a href="/solutions/dry-goods" class="explore-card">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 2h18l-2 7H5L3 2z"/><path d="M5 9l-1 13h16L19 9"/></svg>
                <div>
                    <div class="explore-name">Nuts &amp; Dry Goods</div>
                    <div class="explore-desc">Bulk &amp; weight-based inventory</div>
                </div>
                <svg class="explore-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/solutions/restaurants" class="explore-card">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
                <div>
                    <div class="explore-name">Restaurants</div>
                    <div class="explore-desc">Table management &amp; kitchen flow</div>
                </div>
                <svg class="explore-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sol-cta">
        <h2>Ready to run your store smarter?</h2>
        <p>14-day free trial. No credit card. Set up in under an hour.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
            <a href="/contact?plan=retail" class="btn-primary">Start free trial</a>
            <a href="/features" class="btn-ghost">See all features</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<style>
    :root {
        --teal: #00BFA5;
        --teal-dark: #00897B;
        --teal-light: #E0F7F4;
        --navy: #1A237E;
        --navy-light: #E8EAF6;
        --text: #1C1C1E;
        --text-muted: #6B7280;
        --border: #E5E7EB;
        --surface: #F9FAFB;
        --white: #FFFFFF;
    }

    .sol-hero {
        background: #FFFFFF;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .sol-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        right: -100px;
        bottom: -100px;
        width: 400px;
        height: 400px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,191,165,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .sol-hero-inner {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .sol-eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        background: var(--teal-light);
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,191,165,0.25);
        color: var(--teal-dark);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.09em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 5px 12px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        width: fit-content;
    }

    .eyebrow-dot {
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--teal);
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .sol-title {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.12;
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .sol-accent { color: var(--teal-dark); }

    .sol-sub {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }

    .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
        display: inline-block;
        background: var(--teal);
        color: #FFFFFF;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); }

    .btn-ghost {
        display: inline-block;
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--teal); color: var(--teal-dark); }

    .proof-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .proof-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .proof-avatar {
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--teal-light);
        color: var(--teal-dark);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .proof-name {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
    }

    .proof-role {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .proof-quote {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.65;
        font-style: italic;
        border-left: 3px solid var(--teal);
        padding-left: 0.875rem;
        margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .proof-stat-row {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .proof-stat {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2px;
        border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .proof-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .proof-stat-num {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--teal-dark);
    }

    .proof-stat-label {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .sol-page {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem;
    }

    .pains-section {
        padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .pains-label {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #9CA3AF;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .pains-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .pain-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 10px;
        background: #FFF8F8;
        border: 1px solid #FEE2E2;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .pain-icon {
        color: #EF4444;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .pain-item p {
        font-size: 0.825rem;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.55;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .section-heading {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
        margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }

    .sol-cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .sol-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .sol-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--teal);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,191,165,0.08);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .sol-card-icon {
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .teal-icon { background: var(--teal-light); color: var(--teal-dark); }
    .navy-icon { background: var(--navy-light); color: var(--navy); }
    .green-icon { background: #E8F5E9; color: #2E7D32; }
    .purple-icon { background: #F3E5F5; color: #7B1FA2; }
    .orange-icon { background: #FFF3E0; color: #E65100; }
    .blue-icon { background: #E3F2FD; color: #1565C0; }

    .sol-card h3 {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .sol-card p {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .sol-card-tags {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 6px;
    }

    .tag {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 3px 8px;
        border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .explore-more {
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .explore-more h2 {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .explore-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .explore-card {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--text);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }

    .explore-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal); background: var(--teal-light); }
    .explore-card svg:first-child { color: var(--teal-dark); flex-shrink: 0; }

    .explore-name {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text);
    }

    .explore-desc {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .explore-arrow {
        margin-left: auto;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .sol-cta {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .sol-cta h2 {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    }

    .sol-cta p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }

    .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 700px) {
        .sol-hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 640px) {
        .sol-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .pains-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
</style>
